3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses AI techniques to develop a mobile-based deep learning model for plant disease surveillance. 
4. cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper discusses the performance of the model on real-world datasets, which is relevant to information retrieval tasks.
